race.comment: BETTER BE READY (3) quickly made amends for a narrow defeat at Bowen with a 4.2L win here this grade/trip heavily bet again. Carries just a half kilo more and positions on speed. Well placed to keep winning. THE PENSKE FILE (6) bounced straight back winning this trip/level at Bowen. Presents on a 4-day backup and rates to be right in it. TORQUE ESPAGNA (7) was only beaten 1.2L in the same race making good improvement. Has a handy 2kg claim today and may get closer. FORTIFIED (2) is the remaining runner. He comes back in grade for this with some gear tweaks, but he'd have to find plenty more to threaten.
